rComments: Always late. Class always ran past 9pm and time was never given for project work. Assignments/tests not given back in a timely manner and lacked helpful feedback (i.e. assignments given back 1 week prior to deadline to correct assignment and resubmit with final report). Boring.

While he is a good guy and very friendly, he does not teach very well. He is disorganized - losing class grades, giving no feedback re inital project proposal - so project was done "in the dark" with no input from him. It appears he has taken on too many classes adn cannot keep up. WOuldn't choose a course with him again.
